Basic Use:

To start, open MATLAB and add the downloaded code

e.g.

Add the Toolboxs needed for FDT
>start 

run the asissted method
>fdt_assisted

run the automatic method
>fdt_automatic

discriminates a filament from the persistence criterium: days and tolerance
radius
>fdt_persistence


If you want to perform other tests modify the file fdt_param.m
and execute the corresponding script again.

The following files should not be modified for the proper functioning of the code
fdt_readroms
fdt_filaments
fdt_haversine




Contact:

For more information or suggestions, please contact Osvaldo Artal (oartal@dgeo.udec.cl)
